# game/Scenes/Work/workdressbetter.rpy:6
translate spanish workdressbetter_b2dcfd24:

    # "When I go into Mrs. Mills office, she looks at me with her nose scrunched up, like she just smelled something awful."
    "Cuando entro en la oficina de la Sra. Mills, me mira con la nariz arrugada, como si acabara de oler algo horrible."

# game/Scenes/Work/workdressbetter.rpy:7
translate spanish workdressbetter_8f3aff5b:

    # pc "Is something wrong?"
    pc "¿Pasa algo?"

# game/Scenes/Work/workdressbetter.rpy:8
translate spanish workdressbetter_922562fc:

    # bs "You know that you work in a professional environment, right?"
    bs "Sabes que trabajas en un entorno profesional, ¿verdad?"

# game/Scenes/Work/workdressbetter.rpy:9
translate spanish workdressbetter_9917bac8:

    # bs "Don't you have anything nicer to wear than this outfit?"
    bs "¿No tienes nada más elegante que ponerte que este conjunto?"

# game/Scenes/Work/workdressbetter.rpy:10
translate spanish workdressbetter_a6b99445:

    # bs "You look like a fanny-pack wearing vacation dad."
    bs "Pareces un padre de vacaciones con riñonera."

# game/Scenes/Work/workdressbetter.rpy:11
translate spanish workdressbetter_f1daf0fc:

    # pc "Oh, um... I like these clothes."
    pc "Oh, eh... Me gusta esta ropa."

# game/Scenes/Work/workdressbetter.rpy:12
translate spanish workdressbetter_630696d3:

    # bs "Well I don't. You need to start dressing better at work. Immediately."
    bs "Pues a mí no. Tienes que empezar a vestirte mejor en el trabajo. Inmediatamente."

# game/Scenes/Work/workdressbetter.rpy:13
translate spanish workdressbetter_4af2b761:

    # pc "Okay. I guess I can do that."
    pc "Vale. Supongo que puedo hacerlo."

# game/Scenes/Work/workdressbetter.rpy:15
translate spanish workdressbetter_e5ecd3ed:

    # bs "Just like a nice polo and some slacks are fine. A suit if you're feeling fancy. No jeans, no shorts."
    bs "Basta con un bonito polo y unos pantalones de vestir. Un traje si te apetece ir elegante. Nada de vaqueros ni pantalones cortos."

# game/Scenes/Work/workdressbetter.rpy:16
translate spanish workdressbetter_571316f2:

    # bs "Got it?"
    bs "¿Entendido?"

# game/Scenes/Work/workdressbetter.rpy:17
translate spanish workdressbetter_238bde54:

    # pc "Got it."
    pc "Entendido."

# game/Scenes/Work/workdressbetter.rpy:18
translate spanish workdressbetter_b643f08e:

    # bs "Good. Let's get to work."
    bs "Bien. Manos a la obra."

# game/Scenes/Work/workdressbetter.rpy:19
translate spanish workdressbetter_8c43722c:

    # "The rest of the day passes uneventfully. Until it's time to leave for the day."
    "El resto del día transcurre sin incidentes. Hasta que llega la hora de irse a casa."

